Gazebo Publish from Node Example

This is very simple example of how to publish to a gazebo topic without creating a Publisher.

===================
Build Instructions
===================

 * From this directory:

  $ mkdir build
  $ cd build
  $ cmake ..
  $ make


===================
Execute Instructions
===================

 * Launch gazebo as usual then from the build directory above:

  $ ./publisher_node

 * In gazebo, from the menu bar select 'Window' > 'Topic Visualization'
 * Click the topic you are publishing [~/pose_example]
 * Click ok


